#| msgid "<guilabel>Detection</guilabel>: Select star detection algorithm. Each algorithm has its strengths and weaknesses. It is recommended to keep the default value, SEP, unless it fails to properly detect stars. The following are available:"
msgid "<guilabel>Detection</guilabel>: Select star detection algorithm. Each algorithm has its strengths and weaknesses. It is recommended to use SEP, unless you have a specialized use. The following are available:"
