#. Tag: para
#. +> trunk5
#: ekos-focus.docbook:1143
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Algorithm</guilabel>: This specifies the Critical Focus Zone (CFZ) algorithm. The purpose of this is to calculate the CFZ for the equipment attached in the Optical Train. It is not necessary to use this functionality in order to successfully focus, but it provides useful information if correctly configured."
